  <strong>Extension Version:</strong> 1.1.0</p>
  <h2>Data Source</h2>
  <p>The Utility Man extension uses Sean Lahman's baseball <a href="https://sabr.app.box.com/s/rsry2en86bimvybwsorumfsxmf91002a" target="_blank">database</a> to provide solutions for Immaculate Grid puzzles. This database is publicly available and uses Baseball Reference's `playerID` system to identify players, enabling seamless integration with baseball reference websites like immaculategrid.com.</p>

  <h2>Database Limitations</h2>
  <p>Unfortunately, Sean Lahman's database does not contain all the data needed to solve every Immaculate Grid puzzle condition. The following information is missing from the dataset:</p>

  <ul>
    <li>Player season or career bWAR (Baseball Reference Wins Above Replacement)</li>
    <li>Players who have thrown a no-hitter</li>
    <li>Players who played in the Negro Leagues</li>
    <li>Players who were drafted in the first round of the amateur draft</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data Integration Requirements</h2>
  <p>To integrate this missing data into our existing data models, any dataset must include the necessary information to classify players based on these criteria while maintaining a connection to the Baseball Reference `playerID` column.</p>

  <h2>Available Data Sources</h2>
  <p>The following links provide at least partial datasets for some of the missing conditions, all of which include Baseball Reference `playerID`s:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><a href="https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/WAR_top_ten.shtml" target="_blank">Season bWAR Leaders</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.baseball-reference.com/leaders/WAR_career.shtml" target="_blank">Career bWAR Leaders</a></li>
    <li><a href="https://www.baseball-reference.com/friv/no-hitters-and-perfect-games.shtml" target="_blank">No-Hitters and Perfect Games</a></li>
  </ul>
  <p>With these data sources, combined with the question conditions already solved using Sean Lahman's database, we can solve approximately 98% of all Immaculate Grid puzzle conditions.</p>

  <h2>Missing Data Sources</h2>
  <p>Unfortunately, I have not been able to find similar publicly available sources for the following conditions:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Players who played in the Negro Leagues</li>
    <li>Players who were drafted in the first round of the amateur draft</li>
  </ul>

